                  <summary><p>A multi-text manuscript containing:
    <list rend="numbered">
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vīramāmuṉivar Carittiravaralāṟu</title> (U1). A prose history of <persName xml:lang="en">Constantius Joseph Beschi</persName>, or <persName xml:lang="ta">Vīramāmuṉivar</persName>, composed in 1825 (according to the title). Incomplete.</item>
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vīramamunivar Caritaippuṟaṉaṭai</title> (U2).</item></list></p>

<p>As pointed out by Margherita Trento, these two works have been published by  <persName xml:lang="ta" role="editor">Muttucāmi Piḷḷai</persName> in 1843.</p>

<p>Description by Neela Bhaskar based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed by Emmanuel Francis (January 2023).</p>     </summary>
                  
